name: BMO Money Market Fund
longDescription: BMO Money Market ETF seeks to provide income and liquidity consistent with short-term money market rates while preserving capital by investing primarily in Canadian dollardenominated money market securities and other instruments. The Fund invests primarily in high-quality money market instruments issued by governments and corporations in Canada, including treasury bills, bankers acceptances, and commercial paper.
